      <h1 class="dk-title dk-page-title mb-4">Offline FileSecure Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="dk-lead mb-0">
        Offline FileSecure is designed as a local Android vault. The app does not require an account, does not upload your protected files to a DK App Tools server, and does not include ads or analytics tracking.
      </p>
