  </div>
</section>

<section class="dk-section">
  <div class="container-xl">
    <div class="row g-4">
      <div class="col-lg-8">
        <article class="dk-card">
          <h2 class="h3 dk-app-title mb-3">What the app stores</h2>
          <p class="dk-muted">
            Offline FileSecure stores protected vault data locally on your device. Files added to the vault are stored in the app's local storage area in protected app data. The app may also store local settings such as vault setup state, security preferences, and display preferences.
          </p>

          <h2 class="h3 dk-app-title mt-5 mb-3">No account, cloud upload, ads, or tracking</h2>
          <p class="dk-muted">
            Offline FileSecure does not require you to create an account. The app is designed without cloud upload, advertising SDKs, analytics SDKs, or usage tracking systems.
          </p>

          <h2 class="h3 dk-app-title mt-5 mb-3">Import and export behavior</h2>
          <p class="dk-muted">
            Offline FileSecure uses the Android system file picker for importing and exporting files. When you export a decrypted copy outside the vault, that exported copy is no longer protected by Offline FileSecure and may be handled by the destination folder, storage provider, or other apps you choose.
          </p>

          <h2 class="h3 dk-app-title mt-5 mb-3">Support contact</h2>
          <p class="dk-muted">
            If you contact DK App Tools for support, you may choose to send information such as your email address, question, device details, screenshots, or troubleshooting context. Do not send private vault files or recovery secrets in support messages.
          </p>

          <h2 class="h3 dk-app-title mt-5 mb-3">Children's privacy</h2>
          <p class="dk-muted">
            Offline FileSecure is not designed to collect personal information from children.
          </p>

          <h2 class="h3 dk-app-title mt-5 mb-3">Changes to this policy</h2>
          <p class="dk-muted">
            This privacy policy may be updated as Offline FileSecure and DK App Tools evolve. The latest version will be published on this page.
          </p>

          <h2 class="h3 dk-app-title mt-5 mb-3">Contact</h2>
          <p class="dk-muted mb-0">
            For privacy or support questions, contact DK App Tools at
            <a href="mailto:dkapps.support@proton.me">dkapps.support@proton.me</a>.
          </p>
